# Production Release Gate (Mandatory)

You must output a GO/NO-GO decision with:
- Verification results (what was run / must be run)
- Required env var names (no values)
- DB migration plan + rollback plan
- Observability plan (errors, logs, dashboards)
- Risk assessment (top risks + mitigations)
- Post-deploy monitoring checklist
